description:
DELETE requests to flavors resources are not being translated to the language in Accept-Language

for example, a request to http://somehost:8774/v2/de4e166653544873980bb5df3d079982/flavors/hl with the Accept-Language header set to "ja" results in:

{
    "itemNotFound": {
        "message": "Flavor hl could not be found.",
        "code": 404
    }
}

The message should be translated to Japanese instead of getting the default English response.

